We came to the place she told
us, but...[ML:Dash ] I don't see her...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202907_msg0002

I don't want to think about it,
but could she have collapsed and
be buried in the snow...?[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202907_msg0003
rows.name: If so, we have to save her quickly!
